EuroPlate.ttf
-------------

EuroPlate.ttf is not included in this package. Graphical license plates require the user to
provide their own copy at /config/www/EuroPlate.ttf. Users are responsible for ensuring that
their use of EuroPlate.ttf is permitted by its license.
